	check msgno.
	* src/balsa-index.c: (bndx_change_flags), (bndx_tree_expand_cb):
	ditto.
	* libbalsa/misc.c: (libbalsa_set_fallback_codeset): include
	UTF-8 as a charset.
	* src/balsa-message.c: (mdn_dialog_response): do not clear NULL
	error.

